Is it every month two times or is it every other month?
是每个月两次还是每隔一个月？

139
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,120
All right.
好的。

140
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,200
So exactly.
正是。

141
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:20,280
Just remember the prefix bi- means two.
只要记住前缀“bi-”意味着“二”。

142
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:26,120
And then if it's bi-monthly, bi-annual, bi-weekly, you have to more or less make sure that they
然后如果是“bi-monthly”、“bi-annual”、“bi-weekly”，你或多或少要确保他们

